query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 u1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('c++',
'cron',
'delphi',
'dual-boot',
'environment-variables',
'freebsd',
'memory',
'orientação-a-objetos',
'pipe',
'python-3.x',
'solaris',
'vim',
'winforms')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('pt',
'unix')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Cleanup',
'Explainer',
'Quorum',
'Self-Learner')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
